# 📱 WhatsApp CRM Simulation (MERN + AI)

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project is a **WhatsApp CRM Simulation** built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js). It simulates real-world WhatsApp Business workflows including:

* User onboarding with OTP verification (mocked)
* Template creation with dynamic variables
* Campaign/sequence builder with scheduling logic
* Messaging system with AI-assisted replies
* Chat history storage

⚡ **Note:** No real WhatsApp or Meta APIs are used — everything is simulated via backend logic.

---

## 🧠 Features

### 🔹 1. WhatsApp Onboarding

* User registration form (name, email, phone)
* OTP generation & verification (mocked)
* Simulated Meta verification (Approved / Pending / Failed)

---

### 🔹 2. Template Management

* Create templates with:

  * Header
  * Body
  * Footer
  * Buttons
* Supports dynamic variables (e.g., `{{name}}`)
* Templates stored in MongoDB

---

### 🔹 3. Sequence Builder

* Multi-step flow:

  1. Basic Info
  2. Select Templates
  3. Define Delays
  4. Add Recipients
* Scheduling logic using `setTimeout`
* Simulates real message campaigns

---

### 🔹 4. List Views

* View all templates
* View all sequences
* Toggle active/inactive
* Delete sequences/templates

---

### 🔹 5. AI Chat Assistant (Bonus 🔥)

* AI suggests replies based on customer messages
* Agent can refine responses before sending
* Chat history stored in database

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React (Vite)
* Axios
* Tailwind CSS (or custom CSS)
* Lucide Icons

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB + Mongoose
* Axios (for AI API)

