## ⚙️ Backend Setup

### 1️⃣ Navigate to backend

```bash
cd backend
```

### 2️⃣ Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3️⃣ Create `.env` file

```env
PORT=8000
MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/whatsapp_crm
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
```

### 4️⃣ Start server

```bash
npm run dev
```

👉 Server runs on:

```
http://localhost:8000
```

---

## 🌐 Frontend Setup

### 1️⃣ Navigate to frontend

```bash
cd frontend
```

### 2️⃣ Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3️⃣ Configure API (IMPORTANT)

📁 `src/services/api.js`

```js
import axios from "axios";

const api = axios.create({
  baseURL: "http://localhost:8000",
});

export default api;
```

---

### 4️⃣ Run frontend

```bash
npm run dev
```

👉 Frontend runs on:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

## 🔗 API Endpoints

### 🔹 Auth

```
POST /api/auth/register
POST /api/auth/verify
```

### 🔹 Templates

```
POST /api/templates
GET /api/templates
DELETE /api/templates/:id
```

### 🔹 Sequences

```
POST /api/sequences
GET /api/sequences
PATCH /api/sequences/:id
DELETE /api/sequences/:id
```

### 🔹 Chatbot

```
POST /api/chat
GET /api/chat (history)
```

---

